HTTP
 - request

  - Components
   - HTTP verb/method
   - URL
   - paramaters

  - GET
    - a link or type in an address bar
    - parameters exposed in URL
    - smaller payload

  - POST(form)
    - forms
    - parameters are submitted in body
    - large payload


 
 - response
  - Components
   - status code
   - payload


  - status code
    - 200: ok (HTML..)
    - 302: redirect (URL)
    - 404: file not found
    - 505: general error